In fact, since the anti-aliasing filter of the SDR produces a ùê∫(ùëì)
that is zero for|ùëì|>ùëìùë†/2, and ifùëìùë†‚â™1/ùëáùëèas we just discussed,
the resulting loss of information means that the attacker cannot
