Chronos: Learning the Language of Time Series
Abdul Fatir Ansari1‚àó, Lorenzo Stella1‚àó, Caner Turkmen1, Xiyuan Zhang3‚Ä†, Pedro Mercado1,
Huibin Shen1, Oleksandr Shchur1, Syama Sundar Rangapuram1, Sebastian Pineda Arango4‚Ä†,
Shubham Kapoor1, Jasper Zschiegner‚Ä†, Danielle C. Maddix1, Hao Wang1,5‚Ä†, Michael W.
Mahoney2,6‚Ä†, Kari Torkkola2, Andrew Gordon Wilson2,7‚Ä†, Michael Bohlke-Schneider1, Yuyang
Wang1{ansarnd, stellalo}@amazon.com
1AWS AI Labs,2Amazon Supply Chain Optimization Technologies,3UC San Diego,4University of Freiburg,5Rutgers
